behavior plug_in_toaster(toaster:item):
    body:
        achieve plugged(toaster)

behavior switch_on_toaster(toaster:item):
    body:
        achieve is_on(toaster)

behavior insert_bread_in_toaster(bread:item, toaster:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(bread, toaster)

behavior remove_bread_from_toaster(bread:item, toaster:item):
    body:
        achieve not inside(bread, toaster)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind toaster: item where:
            is_toaster(toaster)
        # Select a toaster
        bind sliced_bread: item where:
            is_food_bread(sliced_bread) and cut(sliced_bread)
        # Select sliced bread

        plug_in_toaster(toaster)
        switch_on_toaster(toaster)
        insert_bread_in_toaster(sliced_bread, toaster)
        # Wait for an appropriate time for toasting to complete
        remove_bread_from_toaster(sliced_bread, toaster)

def is_closed(x: item):
    # Check if an item is closed
    symbol is_it_closed = exists o: item : closed(o) and o == x
    return is_it_closed

behavior ensure_toaster_ready(toaster:item):
    body:
        if exists plug:item: is_powersocket(plug):
            achieve plugged(toaster)
        if not is_closed(toaster):
            achieve closed(toaster)

behavior toast_bread(bread:item, toaster:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(bread, toaster)
        ensure_toaster_ready(toaster)
        achieve is_on(toaster)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind bread: item where:
            is_food_bread(bread) and cut(bread)
        bind toaster: item where:
            is_toaster(toaster)
        toast_bread(bread, toaster)

behavior toast_sliced_bread(sliced_bread:item, toaster:item):
    body:
        achieve plugged(toaster)
        # Ensure that the toaster is plugged in
        achieve inside(sliced_bread, toaster)
        # Insert the sliced bread into the toaster
        achieve is_on(toaster)
        # Turn on the toaster to start toasting the bread

behavior unplug_toaster(toaster:item):
    body:
        achieve is_off(toaster) # Turn off the toaster
        achieve unplugged(toaster) # Unplug the toaster

def put_sliced_bread_in_toaster(sliced_bread:item, toaster:item):
    # Function to put sliced bread into the toaster
    achieve inside(sliced_bread, toaster)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind toaster: item where:
            is_toaster(toaster)
        # Select a toaster
        
        bind sliced_bread: item where:
            is_food_bread(sliced_bread) and cut(sliced_bread)
        # Select the sliced bread

        toast_sliced_bread(sliced_bread, toaster)
        unplug_toaster(toaster) # Unplug the toaster after use
